snippet.title: Business Magnate - Release Trailer (gameplay)
snippet.description:
On Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/950990/Business_Magnate/
Website: https://www.businessmagnate-game.com

This is the release trailer of "Business Magnate", a tycoon business simulation game: Design, produce, and sell cars, rockets, tanks, ships, and others.
